flowchart TD
    A[Scientific papers and dataset records] --> B[Ground truth annotations<br/>validated spreadsheet]
    A --> C[Extraction pipeline<br/>abstract | sections | pdf_native]
    C --> D[LLM predictions<br/>structured fields]
    B --> E[Local evaluation engine<br/>groundtruth_eval.py]
    D --> E

    E --> F[Field-specific graders]
    F --> F1[Exact match<br/>booleans, numeric, controlled vocab]
    F --> F2[Enhanced species matching<br/>vernacular and scientific names]
    F --> F3[Optional fuzzy matching<br/>experimental / fallback]

    E --> G[Metrics and error records]
    G --> G1[Precision]
    G --> G2[Recall]
    G --> G3[F1]
    G --> G4[Exact-match rate]

    G --> H[Run artifacts and review]
    H --> H1[JSON run artifacts]
    H --> H2[Notebook analysis]
    H --> H3[Streamlit eval viewer]

    H --> I[Prompt and pipeline iteration]
    I --> C

    J[Recommended next layer] -.-> K[Locked holdout set]
    J -.-> L[Confidence intervals]
    J -.-> M[Human calibration loop]
    J -.-> N[CI-style continuous eval]
    J -.-> O[Optional OpenAI / HF hosted eval tooling]
